    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……にしても、派手に
やっちゃったんだね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This place...sure is a sight to be seen...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔科学兵器は
デリス・カーラーン全体の
マナを吸い取ったけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This desolate landscape is the result of
Derris Kharlan's Mana supply disappearing
after the Mana Cannon fired.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここは直撃を受けた場所だから、
特にひどいんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This place was directly hit by the
weapon, so it's especially damaged...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275036</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうして、
きみがそんなこと
知ってるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How do you know that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275180</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……なんでかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? I wonder...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275180</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんかぼんやりと
いろんなことが
頭に流れ込んでて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There is a lot of information I shouldn't
know that I can vaguely recall...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレもなんかそんな感じ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I feel the same...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>………………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>故郷がこんなだもんね……
そりゃ必死にもなるか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So this is his home planet...
These sorts of sights are
why he was so desperate...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうして、あの時……
気付けなかったんだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How could I have been
so naive back then...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これって……もしかして……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is this...no way...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mmm...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私の誕生日、
なんで知ってるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How did you know it was my birthday?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>誕生日なのか……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's your Birthday...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　プレゼントじゃないの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So...this isn't a present for me?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276112</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……あはっ、
なんでもいいや。
ありがと、ダオス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Hehe, whatever. Thanks Dhaos!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いや……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's nothing...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……絶対に、
なくすな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Promise me...you won't lose it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もちろん！　大事にするよ！
だって……ダオスがくれた
ものだもん！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Of course! It's my most precious treasure now!
After all...this is a present from you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの日以来、あいつを
森の中で見ることはなくなった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>After that...he never returned
to the forest again...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>思えばあれは
餞別だったのかもしれない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When I think about it now, it's so obvious.
He was giving me a farewell gift.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちゃんとあの時、気付いて、
止められたらよかったのに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I'd known back then...
I'd have stopped him...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_020_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>せめて……
彼の想いを……気持ちを
ちゃんと確かめられれば……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At least... I wish I could have
confirmed his intentions, or rather,
how he felt about me...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
